Manage your private modules with nodejitsu npm

Sign up
Always available, never down

Your private npm registry is hosted on separate replicated infrastructure from the public npm registry for high-availability. Never be down when the public npm registry is down.

Collaborate with your team

Working or managing in a Node.js team? No problem! Our simple access contols make collaborating with them a breeze. All of our hosted private npm registry plans come with unlimited users so your registry can grow with your team.

PhoneGap & Browserify

Your private npm registry will manage more than just Node.js. Building mobile applications with PhoneGap or Apache Cordova? Writing your front-end Javascript with Browserify? Manage them all in one place: your private npm registry.
